commend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-22 10:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855423713,45974302,540]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1134755]icyphoenix[/uid] (2026-01-22 10:23):[/b]<br/><br/>忘了切鱼大的号了这是？[/quote]<br/>再说什么鬼话这是 我就这一个号 连小号都没申请过 封了就没了", "lou": 322, "content_length": 59, "reply_to": 855423713, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769048737}, {"pid": 855424824, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 39, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-22 10:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855424382,45974302,541]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=19752003]eibonyy[/uid] (2026-01-22 10:28):[/b]<br/><br/>关键感觉GJD这一砸感觉作用也不大啊，航天和AI软还是接着舞接着乐，我们业绩股就愣生生挨了一巴掌[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>这边跟GJD关系不大  柚子昨天新进封测 这几天加急拿机构的表格吹，还有封测的延申超额小票，今天全部被机构一巴掌拍地上了<br/>不能再出现航天卫星这种被抢的情况了 尽早拍下来", "lou": 323, "content_length": 160, "reply_to": 855424382, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769049056}, {"pid": 855425073, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 43, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-22 10:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "今天倒也不是说亏多少 ，说实话还没昨天挣的1/5 但是就是恶心  现在就是一个驯化过程<br/>有点不适反应很正常，常年当牛马的大家应该能了解", "lou": 324, "content_length": 121, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769049148}, {"pid": 855426038, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-22 10:38", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855425452,45974302,543]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=7558494]cxq2cxq[/uid] (2026-01-22 10:34):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:哭笑]赵姨都红了5天了，调整一下很正常的，半岛是开盘就整个板块下杀，不是针对存储来的。刚才砸宽基的时候半导体几乎一动不动，当终末帝去[/quote]<br/>你这观察就对了  半导体压盘是机构主压 为了不让封测那边起爆  GJD砸宽鸡根本没有针对科技 也就是机构在提前自纠  防止进来监管<br/>这是合理的 比如那个小票KMKJ  再不压就出现异动了", "lou": 325, "content_length": 160, "reply_to": 855425452, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769049505}, {"pid": 855426717, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 42, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-22 10:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855425874,45974302,543]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66684936]你如何回忆我[/uid] (2026-01-22 10:37):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，要训成啥样啊，我不太懂牛马……[/quote]<br/>GJD ：我给你的 你可以吃  我不给你的  你不能要 我说不行的 你要走 我说行的 你要做", "lou": 326, "content_length": 74, "reply_to": 855425874, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769049739}, {"pid": 855426947, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-22 10:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855426450,45974302,544]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38754660]消费机的逆袭[/uid] (2026-01-22 10:40):[/b]<br/><br/>狼哥能讲下flgf吗，这个什么鬼21连扳。[/quote]<br/>那个是优必选啊  刚出新闻我就说最少15板起步<br/>别人是重组的 和市场没关系 又不会套人 至少这个阶段不会", "lou": 327, "content_length": 95, "reply_to": 855426450, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769049817}, {"pid": 855427700, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-22 10:48", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855427074,45974302,545]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1003090]zzh90pk[/uid] (2026-01-22 10:44):[/b]<br/><br/>不得不感叹狼大的实力<br/>目前我亏掉昨天的8成，而狼大是1/5[s:ac:哭1]<br/>不知道楼里老哥战况如何。[/quote]<br/>你们的选票都是一坨 我虽然也不强 但是总还是强于你们的  而且我善于整合资源", "lou": 328, "content_length": 73, "reply_to": 855427074, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769050106}, {"pid": 855429441, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 34, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-22 10:58", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855428996,45974302,547]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66854697]三蟹[/uid] (2026-01-22 10:56):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，那该咋玩，国家想搞科技，搞各行业龙头，但是科技机构现在又不想柚子拉，那。。。让柚子一起玩定投？[s:ac:咦][/quote]<br/>耐心持仓啊 放弃之前航天AI应用重现那种幻想 一个月吃几个点十几个点不行吗？", "lou": 329, "content_length": 75, "reply_to": 855428996, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769050727}, {"pid": 855429865, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-22 11:01", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855429490,45974302,548]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66734353]长聿[/uid] (2026-01-22 10:59):[/b]<br/><br/>我个人认为这位置调整的不够深，那一路连盈上来的有丰厚的利润垫，怎么也不像这点区间就能震下去呢[/quote]<br/>这不就证明控盘好么  不影响牛市预期 精准打压集体挑战规则的", "lou": 330, "content_length": 59, "reply_to": 855429490, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769050886}, {"pid": 855430663, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 57, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-22 11:05", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855429981,45974302,549]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61973100]Charilily[/uid] (2026-01-22 11:01):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:偷笑]这个月吃12个点我都感激涕零了，竟然还能每个月都这么吃吗，还有这种好事[/quote]<br/>你看 你的思维就和新进股民不一样了 他们是每天要吃这么多 吃不到就是GJD故意针对他", "lou": 331, "content_length": 80, "reply_to": 855429981, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769051154}, {"pid": 855431805, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 31, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-22 11:12", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[img]./mon_202601/22/jmQhp1-1lk1KcT1kSgz-1e.jpg[/img]<br/>割肉?割什么肉？", "lou": 332, "content_length": 53, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202601/22/jmQhp1-1lk1KcT1kSgz-1e.jpg", "size": 12, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202601/22", "name": "jmQhp1-1lk1KcT1kSgz-1e.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769051567}, {"pid": 855433065, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 12, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-22 11:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=855432439,45974302,552]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39810331]a4714280